Armand Assante https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armand_Assante 0 Armand Anthony Assante Jr. (; born October 4, 1949) is an American actor. He is noted for an Emmy Award-winning role as mobster John Gotti in the 1996 HBO Television film Gotti. Armand_Anthony_Assante_Jr. ( ; born October_4_,_1949 ) is an_American_actor .
